'''班哲希利公园'''（Benjasiri Park）是[[泰国|泰国]][[曼谷|曼谷]][[空堤縣|空堤縣]][[素坤逸路|素坤逸路]]上的一个公园，介于22巷与24巷之间，毗邻[[大商場購物中心|大商場購物中心]]及[[鵬蓬車站|鵬蓬車站]] （[[曼谷大眾運輸系統|曼谷大眾運輸系統]][[素坤逸线|素坤逸线]]）<ref>{{cite web |url = http://thailandforvisitors.com/central/bangkok/bkk-parks.html |title = Benjasiri Park |publisher = thailandforvisitors.com |accessdate = 2008-11-13 |archive-date = 2008-12-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081223090231/http://thailandforvisitors.com/central/bangkok/bkk-parks.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>，面积{{convert|11.6|acre|m2}}，1992年8月12日开放，以庆祝[[诗丽吉王后|诗丽吉王后]]六十寿辰。它于1990年开始建设，原为曼谷气象局所在地<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bangkok-thailand-picture.com/benjasiri-park.htm |title=Benjasiri Park |publisher=bangkok-thailand-picture.com |accessdate=2008-11-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080811233346/http://www.bangkok-thailand-picture.com/benjasiri-park.htm |archivedate=2008-08-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.thaiasiatoday.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=112&Itemid=105 | title = Link up with locals in fight to be fit | publisher = ThaiAsiaToday.com | accessdate = 2008-11-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071213163523/http://www.thaiasiatoday.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=112&Itemid=105 | archive-date = 2007-12-13 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。公园环绕一个人工湖而建，有12座泰国艺术家创作的现代雕塑，常用于露天活动<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.lonelyplanet.com/thailand/bangkok/sights/407704| title=Benjasiri Park| publisher=Lonely Planet| accessdate=2008-11-13| archive-date=2009-02-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211175629/http://www.lonelyplanet.com/thailand/bangkok/sights/407704| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

